{"tid":1949913,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"上網睇王弼 莊子唔係好明佢內容，JJ插地求救","createTime":"2020-03-30T03:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T18:29:15.000Z","uid":200200,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"710c3882dd848d2c89725be1bdfa1319e1c92d71","tid":1949913,"uid":200200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:48:30.000Z","msg":"王弼以為「仁義，母之所生，非可以為母」，而母即是道或無。設若有人批評說，無又怎可能生出仁義，如依孟子，仁義是道德心之所發，所謂「由仁義行，非行仁義也」（〈離婁下〉）。你認為王弼會怎樣回答？又這樣的回答有效嗎？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2de2d6c9c4773bf7fca5e4d082b3b042e0219db","tid":1949913,"uid":200200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:51:33.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d47f8db232b0dc8647bac868ffdde8b6d9e4131","tid":1949913,"uid":134863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:53:22.000Z","msg":"讀緊咩？asso?"},{"pid":"725423668710afaccd4f054220ffff8feee319ec","tid":1949913,"uid":200200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d47f8db232b0dc8647bac868ffdde8b6d9e4131","tid":1949913,"uid":134863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:53:22.000Z","msg":"讀緊咩？asso?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:54:59.000Z","msg":"呀sir 開zoom教D唔教D，聽唔明佢UP乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f75900a0d91485f15d6793a51c8ddd7eaecc862","tid":1949913,"uid":14348,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:18:26.000Z","msg":"就咁睇，<br />\n<br />\n王弼 個句想講嘅係：仁義係一個結果/動作，原因係出於道/無。<br />\n<br />\n孟子個邊仁義是道德心之所發，所謂「由仁義行，非行仁義也」。<br />\n<br />\n所以王弼會引用孟子所講答答：道德之心即為道或無，亦如我所言為仁義之母。<br />\n<br />\n王弼所說的「有」和「無」的關係是：「無」是無形無象的，是本，「有」是有形有象的，是末。<br />\n<br />\n因此「有道德之心」係建基於「無」，而一切因道德之心/仁義面行嘅舉動，歸根究底都是建基於「無」。"},{"pid":"f37e8d636a57a486c365f88e9acba5d9cc523dd3","tid":1949913,"uid":54528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學野"},{"pid":"728396a7199346cae5e35ab17fa8de63c5eeb57d","tid":1949913,"uid":298840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T10:57:36.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"7c0f6d155732c9e35c7f3e7281222b25d06acde1","tid":1949913,"uid":203933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d47f8db232b0dc8647bac868ffdde8b6d9e4131","tid":1949913,"uid":134863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:53:22.000Z","msg":"讀緊咩？asso?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:34:55.000Z","msg":"中大"},{"pid":"0919103ac8b0e43d3fdee809fec8e130747c49ff","tid":1949913,"uid":26176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:08:47.000Z","msg":"婦人之仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a31598a144465dde41f06ccefb79c972ef7b100","tid":1949913,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c0f6d155732c9e35c7f3e7281222b25d06acde1","tid":1949913,"uid":203933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d47f8db232b0dc8647bac868ffdde8b6d9e4131","tid":1949913,"uid":134863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:53:22.000Z","msg":"讀緊咩？asso?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T12:34:55.000Z","msg":"中大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:12:08.000Z","msg":"浸中都有類似咁嘅題目 以前有同學就問過我孟子點睇自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa787f488f56972451a7f99f31542f4734dbb34","tid":1949913,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T14:05:16.000Z","msg":"其實即係講緊價值根源嘅問題<br />\n王弼就覺得仁義禮教個價值根源係「道」/「無」<br />\n（王弼雖然係玄學家，但佢係禮法名教嘅既得利益者，<br />\n建制派，梗係講呢啲野。<br />\n不過，上堂考試答問題就唔好寫呢啲喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲老師唔鐘意誅心論）<br />\n<br />\n而家個質疑係，「無」點樣係價值根源？<br />\n咁仁義是道德心之所發」就即係話個根源係道德心<br />\n所以個討論方向就要再問，咁道德心從何以來？"},{"pid":"21a3f2b6c6a3d474c1ff0911bb31ff133de28626","tid":1949913,"uid":185712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T17:23:04.000Z","msg":"你要明白王弼好老子之說<br />\n<br />\n咁就明"},{"pid":"1ffea188dec6cb7a28de026535635de56fb569e5","tid":1949913,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T18:27:08.000Z","msg":"你不如搵返佢成個注出黎睇，可能會明d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8556aab67c7987ca2c6310d85db9e9e7f773510d","tid":1949913,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T18:29:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://books.google.de/books?id=42txBAAAQBAJ&amp;pg=PT71&amp;lpg=PT71&amp;dq=仁義，母之所生，非可以為母&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=sHQo0HWy4O&amp;sig=ACfU3U24hyJb73JUWJ6-Srb8GHfwJiELQw&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwickP2t6cLoAhVvRhUIHR-8CRYQ6AEwAXoECAkQAQ#v=onepage&amp;q=仁義，母之所生，非可以為母&amp;f=false\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.de%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D42txBAAAQBAJ%26pg%3DPT71%26lpg%3DPT71%26dq%3D%E4%BB%81%E7%BE%A9%EF%BC%8C%E6%AF%8D%E4%B9%8B%E6%89%80%E7%94%9F%EF%BC%8C%E9%9D%9E%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%82%BA%E6%AF%8D%26source%3Dbl%26ots%3DsHQo0HWy4O%26sig%3DACfU3U24hyJb73JUWJ6-Srb8GHfwJiELQw%26hl%3Den%26sa%3DX%26ved%3D2ahUKEwickP2t6cLoAhVvRhUIHR-8CRYQ6AEwAXoECAkQAQ%23v%3Donepage%26q%3D%E4%BB%81%E7%BE%A9%EF%BC%8C%E6%AF%8D%E4%B9%8B%E6%89%80%E7%94%9F%EF%BC%8C%E9%9D%9E%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%82%BA%E6%AF%8D%26f%3Dfalse&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYqxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=73b252dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://books.google.de/books?id=42txBAAAQBAJ&amp;pg=PT71&amp;lpg=PT71&amp;dq=仁義，母之所生，非可以為母&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=sHQo0HWy4O&amp;sig=ACfU3U24hyJb73JUWJ6-Srb8GHfwJiELQw&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwickP2t6cLoAhVvRhUIHR-8CRYQ6AEwAXoECAkQAQ#v=onepage&amp;q=仁義，母之所生，非可以為母&amp;f=false</a><br />\n<br />\n其實佢講緊形名關係。幫到你咁多，自己都唔係好熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}